A minor fitness issue meant Jordan Henderson did not feature against West Ham United as a precaution, Jurgen Klopp has confirmed. (@LFC)<br />
<br />
Klopp: &ldquo;Hendo is in outstanding shape as well. He had a few days off in the break, he couldn&rsquo;t train constantly because of different things but it is all good. He should usually play.&rdquo;

